<PolicyPage ID="x59826" Name="Exercise Clothing Policy" Layout="general_Policy.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Policy Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Hart Clothing Policy</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Policy Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Clothing Costs and Building Wear.</Abstract><Date type="date" label="Revision Date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" display="localdateshort" UTC="true">20120425T18:00:00</Date><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Policy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Requirements for BYU-Idaho Approved Exercise Clothing</span></strong> </span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';"></span><span lang="EN" style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #666666; font-size: small; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Come dressed in appropriate attire consistent with the dress and grooming standards of the university.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span lang="EN" style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: #666666; font-size: small; mso-ansi-language: EN; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';"></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Approved BYU-Idaho Hart exercise clothing is required when using the exercise facilities.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Clothing can be checked out in the BYU-Idaho Locker Rooms or purchased at the BYU-Idaho University Store.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">For questions regarding prices at the University Store please call: (208) 496-3400.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">Or visit: <a href="http://www.byuistore.com/c-49-approved-exercise-clothing.aspx">www.byuistore.com/c-49-approved-exercise-clothing.aspx</a></span></div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0.6pt 0in 0.6pt 63.75pt; background: white; mso-list: l2 level2 lfo3; tab-stops: list 1.0in;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;"> </span></p>
