<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: large;"><strong>University Store Discount</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;">The University Store is the only retail provider for approved clothing and will offer a 15% discount on all approved clothing at the beginning of each semester. Clothing can only be purchased by students, employees, or their dependents.  The discount will last through the end of the add/drop period for the semester.  </span> </p>
